 Eskom assures that load-shedding at Stage 4 is no cause for alarm as the system is being effectively controlled.
During Stage 4 load-shedding, approximately 80% of the country’s demand is still being met. Residents are advised to keep checking their load-shedding schedules on the Eskom website: http://loadshedding.eskom.co.za.    Parents frustrated by a lack of space in Middelburg schools Traffic officers to appear in court for corruption #TrafficAlert: Two dead in Kranspoort accidents VIDEO: Two perish after truck jack-knifes • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za